contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary}} '''Omnia''' may refer to: * [[Omnia (band)]], a pagan folk band from the Netherlands * [[Omnia (musician)]], a Ukrainian trance/progressive house dj and producer * [[Omnia Township, Cowley County, Kansas]] * [[Discworld geography#Omnia|Omnia]], a fictional nation in the [[Discworld]] universe * Omnia, a fictional realm in the [[Sudeki]] universe * [[Samsung Omnia]], a group of [[Smartphone|smartphones]] by [[Samsung]] ** [[Samsung Omnia II]] ** [[Samsung i8910|Samsung Omnia HD]] ** [[Samsung Omnia 7]] * Omnia, holiday oven a kind of [[Wonder Pot|Wonder pot]] ==See also== * [[Omni (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}}
